{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #fce4ec; /* Light Pink */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #fafafa;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #c62828;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, #ef5350 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            min-height: 50vh;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #testimonials {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            font-style: italic;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .testimonial-item .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero-section p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .section h3 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .features-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons (optional, but good for features) -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>EdTech Innovate</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n        <a href=\"#testimonials\">Testimonials</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h2>Transform Your Learning Experience</h2>\n        <p>Unlock your potential with our cutting-edge educational platform, designed to make learning engaging, accessible, and effective for everyone.</p>\n        <a href=\"#signup\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"section\">\n        <h3>Our Dynamic Features</h3>\n        <div class=\"features-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                <h4>Expert Instructors</h4>\n                <p>Learn from industry leaders and passionate educators.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h4>Interactive Courses</h4>\n                <p>Engage with hands-on projects and real-world simulations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h4>Progress Tracking</h4>\n                <p>Monitor your achievements and identify areas for growth.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h4>Community Support</h4>\n                <p>Connect with fellow learners and build your network.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"section\">\n        <h3>What Our Learners Say</h3>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n            <p>\"This platform has completely changed how I approach learning. The courses are incredibly well-structured and the support is amazing!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"author\">- Sarah Lee, Student</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n            <p>\"I was able to advance my career significantly thanks to the practical skills I gained here. Highly recommended!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"author\">- John Smith, Professional</div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <h3>Ready to Innovate Your Learning?</h3>\n        <p>Join us and start your journey towards a brighter future.</p>\n        <a href=\"#signup\" class=\"cta-button\">Sign Up Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EdTech Innovate. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JavaScript for smooth scrolling to anchor links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}